{"tid":2260043,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"咬斷警長手指案 控方指被告夠時間作出自主咬噬動作","createTime":"2020-10-27T09:31:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-27T12:31:00.000Z","uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1e1380b84d488cf64846b445d9b0ed61d8cfa146","tid":2260043,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T09:31:22.000Z","msg":"港大畢業生去年7月14日在沙田新城市廣場衝突中涉嫌咬斷偵緝警長梁啟業的手指，早前否認蓄意傷人等罪，今日續審。控方腦神經科專家余毓靈今繼續作供，再次質疑辯方專家的說法，指痛楚及驚嚇反應均不會引起咬噬行為。余又指，根據影片顯示的咬噬時間，相信被告有足夠時間做出自主且有意識的咬噬動作。<br />\n<br />\n余續供稱，根據文獻研究，普遍的單一反應時間為0.2秒，足以讓人經由大腦反應而作出自主行為。根據現場影片，余估計咬噬事件歷時0.66秒，辯方專家則估計是0.46秒，因此被告當時有充足時間有意識地做出咬噬動作。<br />\n<br />\n余在辯方盤問下再次指出，<span class=\"red\">神經學上並無所謂「咬噬反射動作」，當人受到驚嚇時，其典型面部反應是張開口，有時露出牙齒，而非咬緊牙齒</span>。辯方續問，自主反應及非自主的反射反應的分界為何；余稱沒法劃出紅線，非要界定不可是不切實際。"},{"pid":"6c56b15cc860a37f88befb1a6efc7bad43b03f58","tid":2260043,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T09:31:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201027/3UDCWI7Q4JGUBGAXL4I46UC4IQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201027%2F3UDCWI7Q4JGUBGAXL4I46UC4IQ%2F&d=BCqMRPjRs%2BrlYbPtDS4RDBAEDuEYyIgqOvZcTDxqS2A%3D&h=77a75a32\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201027%2F3UDCWI7Q4JGUBGAXL4I46UC4IQ%2F&h=cc647488\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201027/3UDCWI7Q4JGUBGAXL4I46UC4IQ/</a>"},{"pid":"0490a4acb98d709b70753e1fd6ea778b46951ed4","tid":2260043,"uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T09:32:06.000Z","msg":"藍屍 余毓靈<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MEaZhAz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMEaZhAz.jpg&h=1cf06a95&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"51db9d8334ffecba27916bcd796cff93e5d4e287","tid":2260043,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T09:37:48.000Z","msg":"佢地永遠只係討論受驚時情況<br />\n少左樣受驚時如果有異物擺左入口, 個情況會唔會唔同<br />\n如果你眼受到攻擊, 咁你會合埋眼試圖阻擋<br />\n口部情況應同一樣, 而唔係著重眼受襲而受驚所以咬佢"},{"pid":"97737bb3d247024271bc2eb4768daa5cffc6ec3e","tid":2260043,"uid":55897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T09:38:17.000Z","msg":"緊張咬牙切齒"},{"pid":"d497d36c96f0b05e1c583632f580c7fd5738c6e1","tid":2260043,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T09:40:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f047fc850596672f45697f33a1ce40a40a4a126c","tid":2260043,"uid":22556,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T09:40:38.000Z","msg":"幾時見過人驚既時候係 露出牙齒😅"},{"pid":"2869565847dee4af014012cdcf305f93e1ec3bcc","tid":2260043,"uid":158404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T09:41:48.000Z","msg":"黑警講到個個都係超人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16f2be9a3fa0e4d25fed710e5bbe8f563525bdb3","tid":2260043,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T09:44:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"400626310a8f8b1e03a77efccee5aa80ac2ef520","tid":2260043,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T09:46:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b3b887ee243bf16fbbf78deebe3e25e2117e245","tid":2260043,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T09:53:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e8e3afc09804bbab884600b06daf1e5ce13226f","tid":2260043,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0490a4acb98d709b70753e1fd6ea778b46951ed4","tid":2260043,"uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T09:32:06.000Z","msg":"藍屍 余毓靈<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MEaZhAz.jpg\